  "synopsis": "Justin Timberlake and Mila Kunis make witty whoopee as a pair of successful but commitment-shy cynics who agree to take their friendship into the bedroom while leaving all emotional baggage at the door. Unfortunately, it seems that where friends are concerned, there's no such thing as uncomplicated sex. Benefiting from a sharp script, genuine spark between the two leads and fine support from Woody Harrelson, Patricia Clarkson and Richard Jenkins, the director of Easy A makes it two cool and sassy sex-coms in a row.",
